  "detailed_description": "<strong>Once Upon a time,<br>A chicken that dreamed of flying, it tried 30 times... and it fell.</strong><br><br>Fall, dodge obstacles and don't die.<br>The game has 30 stages, 9 skins, relaxing music and good hours of pure fun!<br><br><i>The game features:</i><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>30 amazing and minimalist stages</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>9 different skins</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gamepad support</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Relaxing music (it's not the trailer song)</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The game can help as an anti-stress</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Translation into English and Portuguese</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Good hours of pure fun!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746770/extras/55322339dc214a122bddaa5c3ff49fc5.poster.avif?t=1772548797\" width=534 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746770/extras/55322339dc214a122bddaa5c3ff49fc5.webm?t=1772548797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746770/extras/55322339dc214a122bddaa5c3ff49fc5.mp4?t=1772548797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746770/extras/a0f8c1347bc2bc8c593b9d1250283634.poster.avif?t=1772548797\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746770/extras/a0f8c1347bc2bc8c593b9d1250283634.webm?t=1772548797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746770/extras/a0f8c1347bc2bc8c593b9d1250283634.mp4?t=1772548797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video>